rms.model

Class Location

  • java.lang.Object
    • rms.model.Location

  • public class Location
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is meant to be used with the PRMS database. It is a model class for the Location table in the database Each location is given a unique Location ID. Other information such as city, state, zip, etc. are filled out for each location.
